title.value: Logica COVID-19 FHIR Profile Library IG

description.value: The COVID-19 IG describes structured data to be collected and communicated between providers and aggregators.

name.value: COVID 19 Exposure Core profile

description.value: A parent, abstract profile to be used for the CDC COVID 19 PUI report form exposure section elements.

name.value: COVID 19 Exposure Questionnaire

description.value: A list of questions about one's exposure history for COVID 19.

name.value: COVID-19 gastrointestinal and hepatic underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specific gastrointestinal or hepatic condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 hemoglobinopathy underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specific hemoglobinopathy condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 ICD 10 Diagnosis

description.value: A diagnosis or diagnoses asserted about the subject that is due to infection by the SARS coronavirus 2 virus and using codes specific to the ICD 10 code system.

name.value: COVID-19 immune underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specified immune condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 Immunization

description.value: A profile of the Immunization resource, constrainind some elements to specific to SARS CoV 2 information.

name.value: COVID 19 Vaccine Manufacturer

description.value: A profile of the Organization resource to constain it to vaccine manufacturers.

name.value: COVID-19 renal underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specific renal condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 respiratory underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specific respiratory condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 SNOMED Diagnosis

description.value: A diagnosis or diagnoses asserted about the subject that is due to infection by the SARS coronavirus 2 virus and using codes specifically from the SNOMED CT code system.

name.value: COVID 19 Symptoms Absent

description.value: A parent profile for the assertion of the Absence COVID 19 symptoms.

name.value: COVID 19 Symptoms Present

description.value: A parent profile for the assertion of the presence COVID 19 symptoms.

name.value: COVID-19 uncategorized underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that an uncategorized medical condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 cardiovascular underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specific cardiovascular condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 Underlying Medical Condition observation

description.value: The structure for the observations of named underlying conditions of COVID 19.

name.value: COVID-19 immunocompromised underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specific immunocompromised condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 General Underlying Conditions Absent

description.value: An assertion that generalized conditions such as chronic respiratory disease ARE NOT present along with the COVID-19 disease.

name.value: COVID-19 General Underlying Conditions Present

description.value: An assertion that generalized conditions such as chronic respiratiory disease or chronic metabolic disease are also present with the COVID-19 disease.

name.value: COVID-19 metabolic underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specific metabolic condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: COVID-19 neurologic underlying condition

description.value: An assertion that a specific neuroligical condition is present as an underlier to COVID-19.

name.value: Case-Patient Report Identifying Information

description.value: The identifying information for a reportable disease or condition.

name.value: Coded Laboratory Observation Base

description.value: Abstract base class for coded laboratory observations.

name.value: Exposure Type

description.value: Exposure Type is a description of how, when, where, and with whom and individual was exposed to SARS CoV 2 virus.
